


{"id":2137,"date":"2016-04-19T12:55:27","date_gmt":"2016-04-19T11:55:27","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/?page_id=2137"},"modified":"2025-05-01T23:28:40","modified_gmt":"2025-05-01T22:28:40","slug":"priprava-a-realizace-stk","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/priprava-a-realizace-stk\/","title":{"rendered":"P\u0159\u00edprava a realizace STK"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mp-row-fluid motopress-row mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"motopress-clmn mp-span12  mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"row product-detail\"> <div class=\"span6 \"><h2>Kompletn\u00ed p\u0159\u00edprava a vy\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed STK pro v\u00e1\u0161 v\u016fz<\/h2>\n<p>S\u00a0pojmem <strong>STK<\/strong>, jinak zn\u00e1m\u00fdm jako technickou kontrolou, se za sv\u016fj \u017eivot setkal ka\u017ed\u00fd, kdo m\u00e1 vlastn\u00ed automobil. Jde o ze z\u00e1kona povinnou kontrolu vozidla, kter\u00e1 v\u00e1m p\u0159edur\u010d\u00ed, zda je va\u0161e vozidlo zp\u016fsobil\u00e9 k\u00a0provozu. T\u00e1pete ve v\u0161ech informac\u00edch o <strong>STK<\/strong> ? \u017d\u00e1dn\u00fd strach. V\u0161e vy\u0159e\u0161\u00edme za v\u00e1s.<\/p>\n<p>P\u0159ed pravidelnou technickou prohl\u00eddkou vozidla se vyplat\u00ed v\u011bnovat \u010das p\u0159\u00edprav\u011b. Pokud ji vynech\u00e1te a va\u0161e auto nespl\u0148uje podm\u00ednky kontroly, m\u016f\u017ee v\u00e1s technik <strong>STK<\/strong> odm\u00edtnout. Chcete m\u00edt jistotu, \u017ee je v\u0161e tak, jak m\u00e1 b\u00fdt ? Sv\u011b\u0159te sv\u016fj automobil p\u0159ed <strong>STK<\/strong> do na\u0161ich rukou.<\/p>\n<h2>P\u0159\u00edprava na STK zahrnuje<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Identifikaci vozu podle jeho VIN<\/li>\n<li>Kontrolu \u0159\u00edzen\u00ed<\/li>\n<li>Kontrolu pneumatik<\/li>\n<li>Kontrolu tlumi\u010d\u016f<\/li>\n<li>Kontrolu geometrie<\/li>\n<li>Kontrolu sv\u011btlomet\u016f<\/li>\n<li>\u00a0Kontrolu bezpe\u010dnostn\u00edch p\u00e1s\u016f, airbag\u016f<\/li>\n<li>Kontrolu motoru - diagnostika, m\u011b\u0159en\u00ed emis\u00ed\u00a0 ( sou\u010d\u00e1st STK )<\/li>\n<li>Kontrolu brzdov\u00e9ho syst\u00e9mu \u2013 \u00fa\u010dinnost brzd, koroze<\/li>\n<li>Kontrolu stavu podvozku a jeho sou\u010d\u00e1st\u00ed -\u00a0 koroze a jin\u00e9 mechanick\u00e9 po\u0161kozen\u00ed<\/li>\n<li>Kontrolu stavu karos\u00e9rie - koroze a jin\u00e9 mechanick\u00e9 po\u0161kozen\u00ed<\/li>\n<li>Kontrolu v\u00fdfukov\u00e9ho syst\u00e9mu - t\u011bsnost, koroze<\/li>\n<li>Kontrolu povinn\u00e9 v\u00fdbavy<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Ve\u0161ker\u00e9 nalezen\u00e9 nedostatky jsme schopni na m\u00edst\u011b odstranit. Nab\u00edz\u00edme tak\u00e9 <strong>kompletn\u00ed realizaci STK<\/strong>. Vy n\u00e1m p\u0159ed\u00e1te v\u016fz s doklady ( VTP,ORV ) a my celou kontrolu vy\u0159\u00edd\u00edme za v\u00e1s. U\u017e za 2 hodiny m\u016f\u017ee b\u00fdt hotovo.<\/p><\/div>\n<div class=\"span6 \"><div class=\"motopress-image-obj motopress-text-align-left\"><img src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/autservis-thumb.jpg\" title=\"autservis-thumb\" alt=\"autservis-thumb\" class=\"motopress-image-obj-basic mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right mpce-dsbl-margin-top mpce-dsbl-margin-bottom\" \/><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><!-- .row (end) -->\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"mp-row-fluid motopress-row mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"motopress-clmn mp-span12  mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"content_box call-to-action-row no-margin-bottom \"> <div class=\"row \"> <div class=\"span12 \"><p>P\u0159\u00edpravu vozu k STK i kompletn\u00ed realizaci technick\u00e9 prohl\u00eddky <strong>objedn\u00e1vejte p\u0159edem<\/strong> na telefonn\u00edm \u010d\u00edsle <a href=\"tel:+420 608 313 437\">+420 605 399 448, +420 608 313 437<\/a><br \/>\n(Po-P\u00e1 od 9 do 18 hod.)<\/p><\/div> <\/div><!-- .row (end) --> <div class=\"clear\"><\/div><\/div><!-- .content_